05 14:10:43'),
	(116, 58, 'en', 'Introducing the Global Hallyu Team', '<p data-start="183" data-end="542" style="text-align: justify; ">Hallyu (the Korean Wave) began in the late 1990s as a subcultural phenomenon rooted in Asian cultural identity and fan communities, and has since expanded into a global cultural phenomenon. This expansion reflects both the changing status of Korea in the world and the universal issues of contemporary society embodied and reproduced through Hallyu content.</p><p data-start="544" data-end="1307" style="text-align: justify;">With a critical awareness of the need to reassess the significance of Hallyu and to pursue new avenues of research, the Global Hallyu Team sets out the following objectives. First, we explore how Hallyu, as a transnational cultural phenomenon, reshapes existing theories of global culture, thereby making theoretical contributions. While many case studies have accumulated around Hallyu as a media-mediated and contextually embedded global reception phenomenon, our aim is to move beyond case-specific analysis. We seek to theorize Hallyu in a way that contributes to general knowledge on global cultural production and reception, and to examine academically how intersubjective knowledge about Korea’s place and meaning in the world is produced through Hallyu.</p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p data-start="1309" data-end="1479" style="text-align: justify; ">To achieve this, the team fosters global scholarly networks, advances collaborative research, and is committed to training the next generation of scholars in the field.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-26 11:18:46', '2025-08-20 16:56:19'),
	(117, 59, 'ko', '박소정', '<p style="text-align: justify; "><font color="#000000"><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">한양대학교 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">ERICA </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">문화콘텐츠학과 조교수</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">서울대학교 언론정보학과에서 석</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">·</span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">박사학위를 받은 후</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">대중문화와 디지털 문화에 대해 가르치고 연구한다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. TV, </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">영화</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">아이돌</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">온라인 커뮤니티 등 대중문화와 디지털문화의 전 영역을 꾸준히 향유해 온 덕에 덕업일치를 이룬 연구자가 되었다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">주로 미디어 문화를 통해 관찰되는 정체성과 친밀성의 문제에 대해 관심을 갖고 담론 분석과 인터뷰 등의 질적 방법을 활용한 연구를 수행한다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">특히</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">한류와 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">K-</span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">콘텐츠가 생산되고 수용되는 방식과 그 과정에서 만들어지는 담론 및 가치에 대해 다종의 연구를 수행했다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">또한</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">새롭게 부상하는 디지털 플랫폼이 만들어내는 콘텐츠 특성과 수용자 문화에 대해서도 관심을 갖고 연구 및 교육하고 있다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">저서인 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><</span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">미백</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">: </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">피부색의 문화정치</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">>(2022</span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">년 대한민국학술원 우수학술도서</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">, 2023</span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">년 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">ICAS </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">한국어 우수 학술도서</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">)</span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">를 통해 한국 미디어 문화의 핵심 미학인 미백과 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">K</span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">뷰티에 대해 포스트식민주의적인 해석을 제시했다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">. </span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">이를 바탕으로 한국과 동아시아 사회의 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">‘</span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">종족</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">-</span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">미디어정경</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial;">(ethno-</span><wbr><span style="font-family: Arial;">mediascapes)’</span></span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">에 주목하며 인종</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">·</span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Arial;">종족 문제와 미디어 환경이 교차하여 만들어내는 여러 현상을 관찰 중이다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-family: Arial; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span></font></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-26 11:19:57', '2025-08-20 15:25:10'),
	(118, 59, 'en', 'Park So-Jeong', '<p data-start="3861" data-end="3880" style="text-align: justify;">Professor So-Jeong Park is an Assistant Professor in the Department of Cultural Content at Hanyang University ERICA Campus. She received her M.A. and Ph.D. in Communication from Seoul National University and specializes in popular and digital culture. Having long engaged with TV, film, idol culture, and online communities, she integrates her personal interest with scholarly research. Her work focuses on identity and intimacy as observed through media culture, using qualitative methods such as discourse analysis and interviews. She has conducted extensive studies on the production and reception of Hallyu and K-content, examining the discourses and values generated in the process, as well as the cultural logics of emerging digital platforms. Her monograph <em data-start="4646" data-end="4694">Whitening: The Cultural Politics of Skin Color</em> (2022), awarded the Excellent Academic Book Prize by the National Academy of Sciences, Republic of Korea (2022) and the ICAS Korean Humanities Book Prize (2023), offers a postcolonial interpretation of whitening and K-beauty as central aesthetics of Korean media culture. Building on this, she investigates “ethno-mediascapes” in Korea and East Asia, exploring how issues of race and ethnicity intersect with contemporary media environments.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-26 11:19:57', '2025-08-20 15:25:10'),
	(121, 61, 'ko', '서지영', '<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: Pretendard; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;">서울대학교 아시아연구소 한류연구센터 선임연구원이며 연세대학교 언더우드 국제대학과 국문학과에서 가르치고 있다. 서강대학교 영문학과 학사 및 동대학원 국문학과 석∙박사 학위, 브리티시 컬럼비아 대학교 아시아학 (한국문화사) 박사 학위를 받았다. 현재, 조선시대와 근대 여성예술인들의 존재양식을 통해 대중문화와 젠더의 연관성을 탐색하고 있으며 ‘셀러브리티’의 역사적 형성 과정을 연구하고 있다. 한류를 한국 대중예술∙문화사의 맥락에서 위치 짓는 역사적, 이론적 작업을 모색 중이다. 연구논문으로 “근대 매체와 기생 셀러브리티의 형성: 공적 친밀성 개념을 중심으로” (2023), “1930년대 대중예술의 장과 기생의 공적 재현” (2023), “여악(女樂)의 재현의 층위들: 조선시대 예인으로서의 기녀에 대한 고찰” (2021) 등이 있으며, 단독 저서 『경성의 모던걸: 소비, 노동, 젠더로 본 식민지 근대』(2013); 일본어 번역본 『京城のモダンガル: 消費· 労働·女性から見た植民地近代』(みすず書房, 2016)가 있다. 영역(英譯)한 책으로 Kim Chang-nam, </span><em style="font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: Pretendard;">The History of Korean Popular Culture </span></em><span style="font-family: Pretendard; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;">(Brill, 2025 [forthcoming])가 있다.</span></p><div dir="ltr" style="text-align: justify;"><br style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;"></div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-26 11:22:17', '2025-08-20 15:24:42'),
	(122, 61, 'en', 'Seo Ji-Young', '<p data-start="2539" data-end="3854" style="text-align: justify; ">Dr. Ji-Young Seo is a Senior Research Fellow at the Hallyu Research Center, SNU Asia Center, and teaches at both Underwood International College and the Department of Korean Literature at Yonsei University. She holds a B.A. in English Literature and M.A. and Ph.D. in Korean Literature from Sogang University, and a Ph.D. in Asian Studies (Korean Cultural History) from the University of British Columbia. Her research explores the intersections of popular culture and gender through the lives and artistic practices of women in the Chosŏn dynasty and modern Korea, as well as the historical formation of “celebrity.” She situates Hallyu within the historical and theoretical contexts of Korean popular arts and culture. Her publications include “The Formation of Gisaeng Celebrity and Modern Media: With a Focus on Public Intimacy” (2023), “The Public Representation of Gisaeng in the 1930s Popular Arts Scene” (2023), and “Layers of Representation of Women’s Music (Yeak): Gisaeng as Female Performers in the Chosŏn Dynasty” (2021). She is the author of <em data-start="3595" data-end="3686">Modern Girls of Kyŏngsŏng: Colonial Modernity Seen through Consumption, Labor, and Gender</em> (2013; Japanese translation, Misuzu Shobo, 2016). She also translated into English Kim Chang-nam’s <em data-start="3786" data-end="3825">The History of Korean Popular Culture</em> (Brill, forthcoming 2025).</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-06-26 11:22:17', '2025-08-20 15:28:15'),
