><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">「</span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕;">죽음의 병</span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">」</span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕;">으로부터</span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">｣</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: 0pt;">(2020), </span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">｢</span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕;">김수영과 백낙청의 시학</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: 0pt;">(</span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">詩學</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: 0pt;">)</span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕;">적 대화</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: 0pt;">: </span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕;">하이데거에 대한 이해를 중심으로</span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">｣</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: 0pt;">(2023), </span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">｢</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: 0pt;">9·11</span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕;">과 </span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: 0pt;">3·11, </span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕;">혹은 문학의 그라운드 제로</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: 0pt;">(ground zero)</span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕;">에서</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: 0pt;">: ‘</span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕;">재난문학론</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: 0pt;">’</span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕;">을 위한 시론</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: 0pt;">(</span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">試論</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: 0pt;">) 1</span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕; letter-spacing: 0pt;">｣</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: 0pt;">(2024) </span><span style="font-family: 함초롬바탕;">등이 있다</span><span lang="EN-US" style="letter-spacing: 0pt;">.</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 