	(263, 132, 'ko', '[학술] 정치경제팀 제1회 세미나', '<p></p><p style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: small; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: justify;"><img src="/storage/uploads/summernote/68a55f1864b249.83141970_______2025-08-20_14.37.01.png" style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></p><p><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: small; font-family: " helvetica="" neue";"=""><span style="font-family: " helvetica="" neue";="" font-size:="" 16px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"=""><br></span></span></p><h5><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: small; font-family: " helvetica="" neue";"=""><span style="font-family: " helvetica="" neue";="" font-size:="" 16px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="">◦</span><span style="font-family: " helvetica="" neue";"="">일시: 2024년 12월 13일 (금) 오전 11시&nbsp;<br></span></span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; font-family: " helvetica="" neue";"="" neue";="" color:="" rgb(33,="" 33,="" 33);"="">◦</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: small; font-family: " helvetica="" neue";"="">방식: 온라인/영어&nbsp;</span><br><span style="font-family: " helvetica="" neue";="" font-size:="" 16px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="">◦</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: small; font-family: " helvetica="" neue";"="">제목: Post-crisis Restructuring and Development of Chaebols&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-family: " helvetica="" neue";="" font-size:="" 16px;="" font-style:="" normal;="" font-variant-ligatures:="" font-variant-caps:="" font-weight:="" 400;"="">◦</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: small; font-family: " helvetica="" neue";"="">발표: Sea-Jin Chang (National University of Singapore)&nbsp;</span><br><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Pretendard;">서울대학교&nbsp;</span><span class="il" style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Pretendard;">현대</span><span class="il" style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Pretendard;">한국</span><span class="il" style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Pretendard;">종합</span><span class="il" style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Pretendard;">연구</span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Pretendard;">단은&nbsp;</span><span class="il" style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Pretendard;">현대</span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Pretendard;">&nbsp;</span><span class="il" style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Pretendard;">한국</span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Pretendard;">&nbsp;사회를 심층적으로 이해하고 학문적 교류를 촉진하기 위해 국내외 학술&nbsp;</span><span class="il" style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Pretendard;">연구</span><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-family: Pretendard;">자들이 참여하는 정기 오픈 세미나 시리즈를 개최합니다.&nbsp;</span><br><span helvetica="" neue";"="" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">정치경제팀은 매월 1회 이상의 세미나를 개최할 예정입니다. 현재 내년 3월까지 확정된 세미나 일정을 첨부하니 아래 프로그램을 참고해 주십시오.</span><span helvetica="" neue";"="" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">향후 계속해서 새로운 주제가 추가될 예정이니 많은 관심 부탁드립니다.&nbsp;</span><br><span helvetica="" neue";"="" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">오는 12월 13일 금요일에는 정치경제팀 첫 번째 세미나로 싱가포르국립대학교의 장세진(Sea-Jin Chang) 교수님의 주제 발표와 토론이 예정되어 있습니다. 본 발표에서는 아시아 금융위기 이후&nbsp;</span><span class="il" helvetica="" neue";"="" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">한국</span><span helvetica="" neue";"="" style="font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">의 주요 기업집단인 재벌의 구조적 변화와 리더십 전환을 중심으로, 재벌들이 직면한 환경 변화와 적응 과정이 주요하게 다뤄질 것입니다.&nbsp;</span><br><span style="font-size: small; font-style: normal; font-var