etendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">이번 세미나는 현대 한국 사회에 대한 심층적 이해와 학문적 교류를 증진하기&nbsp;</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">위해 기획되었으며 정치 및 경제 분야의 전문가들과 연구자들이 모여 한국의&nbsp;</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">정치와 경제가 글로벌 환경 속에서 어떻게 변화하고 있는지에 대한 심층적인&nbsp;</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">논의를 펼쳤다.</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: HCRBatang; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);"><br style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all;"></span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">주제 발표는 스테판 해</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 14.1032px; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">거드</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">(Stephan Haggard) (UC San Diego) 명예교수가&nbsp;</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">맡아 "</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 14.1032px; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">민주주의와 개발 한국의 경험과 전망</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">"을 중심으로 현대 한국 정치경제&nbsp;</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">체제에서의 도전 과제와 대응 방안을 제시하였다. 특히 다자규범의 약화 무역&nbsp;</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">정책에서의 안보 고려 강화 전략적 무역 정책 공급망 회복력 수출 및 투자&nbsp;</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">통제, 산업정책의 부활 등 최근 국제 정치경제의 변화가 한국에 제기하는 도전에&nbsp;</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">대해 조망하였다.</span></p><p style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; text-align: justify;"><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);"><br></span></p><p style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; text-align: justify;"><img src="/storage/uploads/summernote/68c3d025125f09.88989956_45.png" style="width: 648px;"><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);"><br></span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: HCRBatang; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);"><br style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all;"></span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">이후 진행된 토론에서는 한국현대종합연구단 참여 교수들이 초청되어 한국</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">정치와 경제의 주요 쟁점에 대한 다양한 시각을 공유하였다 교수들은. 특히&nbsp;</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">한국의 경제 불평등, 정치적 양극화 그리고 글로벌 경제와의 상호작용이 국가&nbsp;</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">발전에 미치는 영향을 논의하며 이에&nbsp;</span><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);">대한 대안과 정책적 시사점을 제시하였다.&nbsp;</span></p><p style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; text-align: justify;"><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);"><br></span></p><p style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; text-align: justify;"><img src="/storage/uploads/summernote/68c3d03c53d5b4.04206483_46.png" style="width: 648px;"><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: rgb(58, 61, 69);"><br></span><font style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-family: inherit !important; font-size: inherit !important; color: inherit !important; line-height: inherit !important;"><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 14.1032px; color: inherit !important;"><br style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all;"></span></font><span style="background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 10.5774pt; font-family: Pretendard; color: inherit !important;">이번 세미나는 온라인 방식으로 영어로 진행되었으며</span><span style="font-family: Pretendard; font-size: 14.1032px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;">(Zoom),</span><span style="font-size: 10.5774pt; background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Pretendard; color: inherit !important;">&nbsp;다수의 참가자가&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5774pt; background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Pretendard; color: inherit !important;">함께할 수 있었다. 또한, Q&amp;A 참가자들은 실시간 세션을 통해 발표자 및 초청&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 10.5774pt; background-position: center center; background-size: cover; background-repeat: no-repeat; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Pretendard; color: inherit !important;">교수들과 활발한 질의응답을 나누며 의미 있는 논의를 이어갔다.</span></p></div></div></div></div><p style="text-align: center; "><br></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2025-08-20 14:39:37', '2025-09-12 16:48:19'),
