	(271, 136, 'ko', '[학술] 정치경제팀 제5회 세미나', '<p></p><div style="text-align: justify;"><br></div><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15.6px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400;"><div style="text-align: justify;"><img src="/storage/uploads/summernote/68a56203bdc208.86199552____________________________________5_poster.jpg" style="width: 100%;"></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><img src="/storage/uploads/summernote/68a5620cd1a244.61951751_Open_Seminar_5_Program.JPG" style="width: 100%;"></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><br></div><div style="text-align: justify;"><div style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; font-family: Pretendard, sans-serif; color: rgb(33, 33, 33);"><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); text-align: start;"><h5 style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">일시: 2025년 3월 14일(금) 오후 4시~6시&nbsp;<br></span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">방식: 온라인/영어&nbsp;</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);"><br></span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">서울대&nbsp;</span><span class="il" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">현대</span><span class="il" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">한국</span><span class="il" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">종합</span><span class="il" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">연구</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">&nbsp;</span><span class="il" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">정치</span><span class="il" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">경제</span><span class="il" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">팀</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34);">에서 주최하는 정기 오픈 세미나 시리즈의 다섯 번째 세션을 안내드립니다.</span><font color="#222222" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 15.6px;"><br></span></font><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">이번 세미나는&nbsp;</span><span class="il" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">한국</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">의&nbsp;</span><span class="il" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">경제</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">&nbsp;발전 경험을 글로벌 시각에서 조망하며 이를 통해 선진국과 개발도상국에 미치는 영향을 분석합니다. 특히,&nbsp;</span><span class="il" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">한국</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">의 기술‧산업 전환 과정과 사회적 파트너십 실패 사례를 중심으로&nbsp;</span><span class="il" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">한국</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">&nbsp;</span><span class="il" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">정치</span><span class="il" style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">경제</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">의 구조적 변화를 고찰하고 그 정책적 함의를 심층적으로 탐색할 예정입니다.</span><font color="#222222" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 15.6px;"><br></span></font><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">발표자 1: Elizabeth Thurbon (UNSW Sydney)<br></span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">주제: "What Developed Countries Can Learn from South Korea"</span><font color="#222222" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 15.6px;"><br></span></font><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">발표자 2: Tat Yan Kong (SOAS University of London)<br></span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">주제: “The Failure of Social Partnership in Korea”</span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;"><br></span><span style="font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; font-size: 15.6px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">여러분의 많은 관심과 적극적인 참여를 부탁드립니다.</span></h5></span></